---
import img1 from '../images/basket.webp';
import img2 from '../images/maps.webp';
import img3 from '../images/Cloud.png';
import img4 from '../images/airplane.png'

---

<div class="relative w-full h-full">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Sobre mí</p>
        <div class="py-4 grid gap-3 grid-cols-2">
            <div class="grid gap-3">
                <div class="bg-black py-5 px-5 text-white rounded-3xl flex items-center">
                    <p class="text-xs">Me apasiona el diseño web y siempre busco formas de aprender y de crecer. Me considero una persona dedicada a su trabajo y disfruto mucho el jugar baloncesto.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border relative">
                    <img class="object-cover h-auto " src={img1.src} alt="">
                </div>  
            </div>

            <div class=" rounded-3xl overflow-hidden relative border flex">
                <img class="object-cover h-full max-w-full" src={img2.src} alt="">

                <p class="bg-white/60 absolute bottom-2 left-2 text-xs p-2 border rounded-3xl">Piura, Perú</p>

                <img class="absolute inset-0 top-4 animate-[wiggle_10s_linear_infinite] " src={img3.src} alt="">

                <img class="absolute inset-0 top-1 animate-[wiggle_6s_linear_infinite] " src={img3.src} alt="">

                <div class="absolute inset-0 top-12 animate-[wiggle_8s_linear_infinite] ">
                    <img class=" bottom-0 transform rotate-45 size-8 " src={img4.src} alt="">
                </div>

            </div>
        
        
    </div>
</div>

